BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 183.12 750 Td (FOR HUSBANDS: HOW TO SUPPORT HER) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 735 m 540 735 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 710 Td (1. Listen without trying to fix. Just be present.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 685 Td (2. Don't say 'just pray more' or 'have more faith.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 660 Td (3. Ask 'How can I help right now?' instead of assuming.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 635 Td (4. Learn her warning signs so you can support early.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 610 Td (5. Encourage her therapy - it's not a lack of faith.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 585 Td (6. Pray WITH her, not AT her.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 560 Td (7. Be patient. Recovery is not linear.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 535 Td (8. Celebrate small victories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 510 Td (9. Take care of yourself too - you can't pour from empty.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 11 Tf 72 485 Td (10. Love her like Christ loves the church \(Eph 5:25\).) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F5 10 Tf 72 450 Td (Ephesians 5:25 - Husbands, love your wives as Christ loved the church.) Tj ET

endstream
